 "por": {
  "por_cntn": "<div class=\"porColContainerWBG\">\n<div class=\"porContentCol\"><p class=\"Paragraph SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: auto 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-kerning: none; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 20.5042px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">Studies across the STEM disciplines have shown that student engagement and active learning improve student attitudes, retention, and understanding (e.g., Fry, 2014; Freeman et al., 2014; National Research Council, 2012; and references therein), with greater impact on women and previously low-achieving students (Kogan &amp; Laursen, 2014; Laursen et al., 2014). Nevertheless, implementation of these techniques has been limited and often isolated. The goal of this project was to </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">use a faculty-driven grassroots approach to driv</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">e</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> change in departmental culture about the use of active and collaborative techniques in </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">the classroo</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">m</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">.&nbsp;</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 20.5042px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; color: #000000;\">\r\n<p class=\"Paragraph SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: auto 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-kerning: none; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px;\"><span class=\"EOP SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 20.5042px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; color: #000000;\">\r\n<p class=\"Paragraph SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: auto 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-kerning: none; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px;\"><strong><span class=\"TextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 20.5042px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">Intellectual </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">M</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">erit</span></span><span class=\"EOP SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 20.5042px;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; clear: both; cursor: text; overflow: visible; position: relative; direction: ltr; color: #000000;\">\r\n<p class=\"Paragraph SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: auto 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; vertical-align: baseline; font-kerning: none; background-color: transparent; color: windowtext; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px;\"><span class=\"TextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; font-variant-ligatures: none !important; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 20.5042px;\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">This effort targeted large-enrollment introductory courses </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">with multiple sections and instructors</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">. By using a course-based</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> model</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> rather than </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">an </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">instructor-based model</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">,</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> the project was able to engage with a mu</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">ch larger group of </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun ContextualSpellingAndGrammarErrorV2Themed SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text; background-position: 0px 100%; background-repeat: repeat-x; background-image: var(--urlContextualSpellingAndGrammarErrorV2,url(;\">faculty</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> than might have otherwise </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">been</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> involved in </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">a teaching reform</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> effort.</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">Many of the barriers to change </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">we</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\">identified</span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW70593619 BCX8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; user-select: text;\"> were not </span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW